Class T_Generic

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.derbyTesting.unitTests.harness.T_Generic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.derby.iapi.services.monitor.ModuleControl, UnitTest
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    T_AccessFactory, T_CacheService, T_Cipher, T_Heap, T_Like, T_MarkedLimitInputStream, T_MultiIterations, T_RecoverBadLog, T_RecoverFullLog, T_Recovery, T_SortController, T_UUIDFactory, T_XA

    public abstract class T_Generic
extends java.lang.Object
implements UnitTest, org.apache.derby.iapi.services.monitor.ModuleControl
    Abstract class which executes a unit test.

    To write a test, extend this class with a class which implements the two abstract methods:

    • runTests
    • setUp
    See Also:
    UnitTest, ModuleControl
